Installations

  1. After unzip the download pack, you'll found a helpyea_maida_ticket_system.zip.
  2. Now go to your cpanel or open your FTP Client (like Filezilla) and upload the content of the Template on your server's root directory.(public_html)
  3. Once the files are done uploading go to .env file open it and edit it
  4. Change configration according to your need

 

 

  1. after filling all information save the file and then go to Terminal

 

  1. when terminal opens then type the following commands say that we have unzip file in public_html
cd public_html

php artisan key:generate 
php artisan migrate
php artisan config:cache

now open in browser new tab yourdomain.com/register

Grant rights to user for admin

  1. register a user by filling a from
  2. now in cpanel go to php my admin

 

Click on your database

click on users

click on edit

you will found a row named as role

that is written as normal

edit it and write

admin

 

scroll to bottom and click Go

now open yourdomain/admin

Alternative i have provided sql file just import that in you database

 

 

 

Configrations

This screen will come up to you

first you need to set up logo and all details for the website

go to setting-> Site setting

 

 

After editing all click on save and it will save all data.

 

Add departments

Click on department Clik on add department

fill the details these departments are assigned to tickets and mangers

 

 

Add Page / Faqs

Click on Settings -> Pages/faqs
there is a dropdown .. Select Identity
faq / Page / Homepagetagline1 /Homepagetagline2

Homepagetagline1 is in home page top tag line.

 

Homepagetagline2

 

 

To change these just select identity and title and content

 

then click on save it will change on frontend also the letest will show up on website

 

You can also create pages as you want same just select the identity to page

 

Same for the faqs

User rights

Go to users

click on edit

Change user type to admin / manager / user

 

 

 

Create a Manger other wise every ticket is going to assigned to admin

 

also have active and inactive state for user to block a user from every thing

Manger dashboad

 

 

assign ticket

click on tickets

click on ticket id

assgin a manger to ticket or a department to ticket after that manger is able to post a reply

email notification are auto genrated for  new ticket , manger assign , reply , opened, closed etc
